    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Handcrafted textiles made in the city of Korhogo in the northern part of Côte d'Ivoire. The painted cloth is characterized by stylized human and animal forms. The images are hand-painted in dark brown dye on narrow strips that are sewn together to form larger sheets of cloth. Handcrafted textiles made in the city of Korhogo in the northern part of Côte d'Ivoire. The painted cloth is characterized by stylized human and animal forms. The images are hand-painted in dark brown dye on narrow strips that are sewn together to form larger sheets of cloth.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
